queries.sql: SELECT u.id, emp_id, first_name, middle_name, last_name, gender, email, contact, position, type_of_contract, d.name as department_name, r.name as role_name, status, user_archived FROM users u JOIN departments d ON u.department_id = d.id JOIN roles r ON u.role_id = r.id WHERE u.user_delete = 0 AND u.user_archived = 0

timelineData.name: Query
timelineData.query: SELECT u.id, emp_id, first_name, middle_name, last_name, gender, email, contact, position, type_of_contract, d.name as department_name, r.name as role_name, status, user_archived FROM users u JOIN departments d ON u.department_id = d.id JOIN roles r ON u.role_id = r.id WHERE u.user_delete = 0 AND u.user_archived = 0
